            <title>[JXR-103] All DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional references are incorrect</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/JXR-103</link>
                <project id="12317527" key="JXR">Maven JXR (Moved to GitHub Issues)</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Velocity templates contain:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;tt&gt;&amp;lt;!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC &quot;-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN&quot; &quot;DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

